<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Investment Incentive Gap | Canada vs UK vs US</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --canada: #e05264;
            --uk: #3b82f6;
            --us: #8b5cf6;
            --accent: #0d9488;
            --light-gray: #f3f4f6;
            --mid-gray: #9ca3af;
            --dark-gray: #374151;
            --text-black: #111827;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', sans-serif;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: var(--text-black);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
            color: var(--text-black);
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-black);
        }

        p, li {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--dark-gray);
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }

        a:hover {
            border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem);
            color: var(--mid-gray);
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        section {
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light-gray);
        }

        section:last-of-type {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f9fafb 100%);
        }

        .hero .subtitle {
            max-width: 750px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .updated-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* Fade-in animation */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards; }
        section { opacity: 0; }
        section.is-visible { animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out; opacity: 1; }

        /* KPI Cards */
        .kpi-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .kpi-card {
            background: var(--light-gray);
            padding: 1.75rem;
            border-radius: 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--mid-gray);
        }

        .kpi-card.canada { border-top-color: var(--canada); }
        .kpi-card.uk { border-top-color: var(--uk); }
        .kpi-card.us { border-top-color: var(--us); }
        .kpi-card.gap { border-top-color: var(--accent); }

        .kpi-value {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin: 0.75rem 0;
            color: var(--text-black);
        }

        .kpi-label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--mid-gray);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .kpi-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--dark-gray);
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .cite {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--mid-gray);
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .cite a {
            color: var(--mid-gray);
            border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--mid-gray);
        }

        .cite a:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
            border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Flow containers */
        .flow-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .flow-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .flow-column {
            padding: 2rem;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-left: 4px solid;
        }

        .flow-column.canada { border-left-color: var(--canada); }
        .flow-column.uk { border-left-color: var(--uk); }
        .flow-column.us { border-left-color: var(--us); }

        .flow-column h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .flow-column h3::before {
            content: '';
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: currentColor;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .flow-column.canada h3 { color: var(--canada); }
        .flow-column.uk h3 { color: var(--uk); }
        .flow-column.us h3 { color: var(--us); }

        .flow-steps {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }

        .flow-step {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .flow-step-number {
            min-width: 28px;
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid currentColor;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .flow-column.canada .flow-step-number { color: var(--canada); border-color: var(--canada); }
        .flow-column.uk .flow-step-number { color: var(--uk); border-color: var(--uk); }
        .flow-column.us .flow-step-number { color: var(--us); border-color: var(--us); }

        .flow-step-text { padding-top: 0.15rem; }
        .flow-step-text p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }

        /* Tabs */
        .tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .tab-button {
            padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--light-gray);
            background: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-radius: 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            color: var(--mid-gray);
        }

        .tab-button:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
        .tab-button.active { background: var(--accent); color: white; border-color: var(--accent); }

        .tab-content { display: none; }
        .tab-content.active { display: block; }

        .scenario-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-black);
        }

        .bar-chart-row { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

        .bar-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--dark-gray);
        }

        .bar-container {
            height: 52px;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .bar-segment {
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            padding: 0 0.5rem;
            transition: flex-basis 0.3s ease;
        }

        .bar-segment.benefit { background: var(--accent); }
        .bar-segment.cost { background: #ef4444; }
        .bar-segment.gain { background: #10b981; }
        .bar-segment.us-gain { background: var(--us); }

        .bar-total {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 0.4rem;
            color: var(--text-black);
        }

        .bar-total.positive { color: #059669; }
        .bar-total.negative { color: #dc2626; }

        /* Sector gap */
        .sector-visual {
            margin: 2rem 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sector-visual { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .sector-bar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

        .sector-bar-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--dark-gray);
        }

        .sector-bar-visual {
            height: 70px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2px;
            align-items: stretch;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .sector-bar-visual.narrow { gap: 0; }

        .sector-segment {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.4rem;
        }

        .sector-segment.mining { background: var(--canada); flex: 0 0 100%; }
        .sector-segment.tech { background: #6366f1; }
        .sector-segment.lifesci { background: #8b5cf6; }
        .sector-segment.cleantech { background: #06b6d4; }
        .sector-segment.manufacturing { background: #ec4899; }
        .sector-segment.services { background: #f59e0b; }
        .sector-segment.ai { background: var(--uk); }

        .sector-gap-text {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-black);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* Holding structures section */
        .holding-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .holding-card {
            padding: 1.75rem;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-top: 4px solid var(--canada);
        }

        .holding-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .holding-card .hold-period {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--canada);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .holding-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .holding-card.highlight {
            border-top-color: var(--accent);
            background: #f0fdfa;
        }

        .holding-card.highlight .hold-period {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Models */
        .models-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .models-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .model-card {
            padding: 2rem;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-left: 4px solid;
        }

        .model-card.fts { border-left-color: var(--canada); }
        .model-card.eis { border-left-color: var(--uk); }

        .model-card h3 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

        .timeline { position: relative; padding: 1rem 0; }

        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 6px;
            top: 28px;
            width: 2px;
            height: calc(100% + 0.5rem);
            background: var(--light-gray);
        }

        .timeline-item:last-child::before { display: none; }

        .timeline-dot {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-top: 4px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .model-card.fts .timeline-dot { background: var(--canada); }
        .model-card.eis .timeline-dot { background: var(--uk); }

        .timeline-text { padding-top: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .timeline-text strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }

        .model-stat {
            background: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .model-stat strong { color: var(--text-black); }

        /* Gap analysis */
        .gap-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .gap-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .gap-column { padding: 2rem; background: var(--light-gray); }

        .gap-column h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .gap-column.uk h3 { color: var(--uk); }
        .gap-column.missing h3 { color: var(--canada); }

        .gap-column h3::before { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; }
        .gap-column.uk h3::before { content: '\2713'; color: var(--uk); }
        .gap-column.missing h3::before { content: '\2717'; color: #ef4444; }

        .gap-list { list-style: none; }

        .gap-list li {
            padding: 0.6rem 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding-left: 1.75rem;
            position: relative;
            color: var(--dark-gray);
        }

        .gap-list li::before {
            content: '\2713';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .gap-column.uk .gap-list li::before { color: var(--uk); }
        .gap-column.missing .gap-list li::before { content: '\2717'; color: #ef4444; }

        /* Path forward */
        .path-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .path-card {
            padding: 1.75rem;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .path-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

        .path-step-number {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .path-card p { flex: 1; font-size: 0.9rem; }

        /* CEI callout */
        .callout {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .callout h3 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .callout p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* QSBS callout */
        .callout-us {
            background: #f5f3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--us);
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .callout-us h3 {
            color: var(--us);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .callout-us p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .sources-grid {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sources-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .sources-column h4 {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: var(--dark-gray);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .sources-column ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .sources-column li {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--mid-gray);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .sources-column li a {
            color: var(--mid-gray);
            border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--mid-gray);
        }

        .sources-column li a:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
            border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--mid-gray);
            margin-top: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .container { padding: 1rem; }
            section { padding: 2.5rem 1rem; }
            .hero { padding: 3rem 1rem; }
            .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
            h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <span class="updated-tag">Updated March 2026</span>
            <h1>The Investment Incentive Gap</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">How Canada's flow-through shares compare to the UK's EIS/SEIS and the US QSBS exclusion &mdash; and why Canada has no innovation investor incentive</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 1: Big Picture -->
    <section id="section-1">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>The Big Picture</h2>
            <div class="kpi-grid">
                <div class="kpi-card uk">
                    <div class="kpi-label">UK EIS/SEIS Annual Raise</div>
                    <div class="kpi-value">&pound;1.82B</div>
                    <div class="kpi-subtitle">~C$3.2B across 6,070 companies</div>
                    <div class="cite"><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/enterprise-investment-scheme-seed-enterprise-investment-scheme-and-social-investment-tax-relief-may-2025/enterprise-investment-scheme-seed-enterprise-investment-scheme-and-social-investment-tax-relief-statistics-2025">HMRC 2025</a></div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-card canada">
                    <div class="kpi-label">Canada FTS Annual Raise</div>
                    <div class="kpi-value">~C$1.0B</div>
                    <div class="kpi-subtitle">~670 companies &mdash; mining &amp; energy only</div>
                    <div class="cite"><a href="https://www.mining.com/canadas-flow-through-shares-surge-despite-capital-gains/">Mining.com 2024</a></div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-card us">
                    <div class="kpi-label">US QSBS Gains Excluded</div>
                    <div class="kpi-value">$152B</div>
                    <div class="kpi-subtitle">2012&ndash;2022 cumulative; 100% federal CGT exclusion</div>
                    <div class="cite"><a href="https://home.treasury.gov/system/files/131/WP-127.pdf">US Treasury WP 127</a></div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-card gap">
                    <div class="kpi-label">Canada Innovation Incentive</div>
                    <div class="kpi-value">$0</div>
                    <div class="kpi-subtitle">No EIS, no QSBS, CEI eliminated in Budget 2025</div>
                    <div class="cite"><a href="https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/2026-tax-measures-changes-new-9.7022831">CBC Jan 2026</a></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2: How It Works -->
    <section id="section-2">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>How Each Scheme Works</h2>
            <div class="flow-container">
                <div class="flow-column canada">
                    <h3>Canada FTS</h3>
                    <div class="flow-steps">
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">1</div>
                            <div class="flow-step-text">
                                <p><strong>Company issues shares at 20&ndash;30% premium</strong></p>
                                <p>Mining/energy explorer uses FTS structure</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">2</div>
                            <div class="flow-step-text">
                                <p><strong>Incurs &amp; renounces exploration expenses</strong></p>
                                <p>CEE/CDE expenses flow through to investor</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">3</div>
                            <div class="flow-step-text">
                                <p><strong>100% deduction + METC/OFFTS credits</strong></p>
                                <p>~73% effective subsidy (Ontario top bracket)</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">4</div>
                            <div class="flow-step-text">
                                <p><strong>Exit via LP rollover or same-day charity</strong></p>
                                <p>Nil cost base &mdash; full proceeds taxable as gains</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flow-column uk">
                    <h3>UK EIS / SEIS</h3>
                    <div class="flow-steps">
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">1</div>
                            <div class="flow-step-text">
                                <p><strong>Invest in qualifying SME</strong></p>
                                <p>Virtually any sector; up to &pound;1M (EIS) / &pound;200K (SEIS)</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">2</div>
                            <div class="flow-step-text">
                                <p><strong>Income tax credit: 30% (EIS) / 50% (SEIS)</strong></p>
                                <p>Immediate reduction in tax bill</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">3</div>
                            <div class="flow-step-text">
                                <p><strong>Hold 3+ years</strong></p>
                                <p>Credit clawed back if sold early</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">4</div>
                            <div class="flow-step-text">
                                <p><strong>Full CGT exemption + loss relief on income</strong></p>
                                <p>Expanding April 2026: &pound;10M / &pound;24M limits</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flow-column us">
                    <h3>US QSBS (&sect;1202)</h3>
                    <div class="flow-steps">
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-step-number">1</div>
